WEBVTT

1
00:11:00.220 --> 00:11:01.270 
叫我吉米就好
Oh, just "Jimmy" is fine.

2
00:11:01.270 --> 00:11:03.300 
吉米  很高兴见到你  快过来
Jimmy, pleasure. Come on down.

3
00:11:03.390 --> 00:11:04.310 
请坐
Have a seat.

4
00:11:05.520 --> 00:11:07.550 
亨利给你讲了我们在找什么样的人吧
Guessing Henry filled you in on what we're looking for.

5
00:11:07.550 --> 00:11:09.390 
他告诉我了
Oh, he did, indeed -- um

6
00:11:09.390 --> 00:11:11.230 
挨个办公室串的推销员
office-to-office salesman

7
00:11:11.230 --> 00:11:14.050 
能接受吃无数的闭门羹
willing to have multiple doors slammed in my face

8
00:11:14.050 --> 00:11:15.510 
只有一个任务
with one mission --

9
00:11:15.650 --> 00:11:18.520 
把他们的旧复印机升级  升级  升级成
upgrade, upgrade, upgrade their old copiers

10
00:11:18.520 --> 00:11:20.320 
你们的最新款
to your top-of-the-line new ones.

11
00:11:20.670 --> 00:11:22.080 
你觉得自己有这个本事吗
Well, you think you have the chops?

12
00:11:22.190 --> 00:11:24.090 
说得容易做起来可难多了
It's a lot harder than it sounds.

13
00:11:24.090 --> 00:11:26.000 
我很愿意尝试一下
Well, I'd sure love a crack at it.

14
00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:27.950 
人们都说  顽强  有说服力
I've been told stubbornness and persuasiveness

15
00:11:27.950 --> 00:11:29.960 
是我最突出的两个特点
are two of my top qualities.

16
00:11:30.220 --> 00:11:32.720 
我得说  吉米很了解复印机
I have to say, Jimmy does know his way around a copier.

17
00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:33.840 
是吗
No kidding.

